data.description: ***Potential Income Earner*** Charming 1947 home located in downtown Prineville close to schools, parks and shops! This home has been meticulously maintained by the current owner and would make for a great first time home or investment property. The first level of the home is 1275Sqft and features a 3 bed 1 bath layout with seasoned hardwood floors, larger living room space and generously sized kitchen. In the back of the home you will find a nicely landscaped gathering area and mature garden in the front. The Second story of this home boasts an additonal 400sqft ADU/guest quarters with separate entrance that has been used as an Airbnb with excellent returns!  The unfinished basement contains a newer gas furnace as of 2021 and is a great place for additional storage.
